<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.9">
<l>vantā yeṉmaṉam pukuntāy maṉṉiniṉṟāy</l>
<l>nantā takoḻuñ cuṭarē yeṅkaḷnampī</l>
<l>cintā maṇiyē tiruvēṅ kaṭammēya</l>
<l>ventā yiṉiyā ṉuṉṉaiyeṉ ṟumviṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who came, who entered my heart, who stays permanently,</l>
<l>Undiminished full sun, our prince,</l>
<l>Cintāmaṇi, our father who dwells in Tiruvēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l>Sweet one, I will not ever let you go!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
